What will result from running the following trace code?
```java
try (DataOutputStream output = new DataOutputStream(new FileOutputStream("temp.dat"))) {
    output.writeInt(100);
    output.writeDouble(50.5);
}

try (DataInputStream input = new DataInputStream(new FileInputStream("temp.dat"))) {
    System.out.println(input.readDouble());
    System.out.println(input.readInt());
}
```

In the following trace code, how many bytes are written to the file?
```java
DataOutputStream output = new DataOutputStream(new FileOutputStream("test.dat"));
output.writeChar('A');
output.writeChar('B');
output.close();
```
